column1: The Patch Status (Detailed) report provides information on devices that have missing patches and on the severity of missing patches. It includes a summary report of the status of patches, failed patch installation attempts, and a list of patches per devices that can be filtered by age of the missing patches or by patches applied within a specified time period.
